column5: I'm looking for a place to launch my boat, I perfer the parking is not $20 like Innisfil Park. I found Island Grove marina, how do they charge? Are there other launched I should look into?  Thanks for any info  I'll be heading out this afternoon and my first attempt at Whities and Lakers. Reports will come very soon.

The cheapest is beside Lake Simcoe Marina,It's FREE,but you gotta park 2 blocks away for FREE.It's between the 4th and 5th on the west side,south of Inninfil Park.....Hope this helps ,TC and tight lines..........Chuck......
